---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Disclaimers | HPSC"
	description="Important disclaimers and limitations regarding the Home Performance Stakeholder Council's services and information."
	keywords="disclaimers, legal notices, limitations, HPSC"
	breadcrumbs={[{ label: 'Disclaimers', href: '/disclaimers' }]}
>
	<div class="w-full">
		<!-- Header -->
		<div class="mb-12">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Disclaimers</h1>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Last Updated: January 2025</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Content -->
		<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 prose prose-lg max-w-none">
			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">General Disclaimer</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					The information provided on this website is for general informational purposes only. While
					the Home Performance Stakeholder Council (HPSC) strives to ensure the accuracy and
					reliability of the information presented, we make no representations or warranties of any
					kind, express or implied, about the completeness, accuracy, reliability, suitability, or
					availability of the information, products, services, or related graphics contained on this
					website.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">No Professional Advice</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					The content on this website does not constitute professional advice and should not be
					relied upon as such. The information provided is not intended to replace professional
					consultation with qualified experts in energy efficiency, construction, legal, financial,
					or other specialized fields.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					For specific advice tailored to your situation, please consult with:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Licensed contractors for construction and renovation work</li>
					<li>Energy advisors for energy efficiency assessments</li>
					<li>Legal professionals for legal matters</li>
					<li>Financial advisors for financial decisions</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Contractor Directory Disclaimer</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					The HPSC maintains a directory of contractors who have met certain certification
					requirements. However:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>
						Inclusion in our directory does not constitute an endorsement or recommendation of any
						specific contractor
					</li>
					<li>
						HPSC is not responsible for the work performed by contractors listed in our directory
					</li>
					<li>
						We do not guarantee the quality, timeliness, or results of any services provided by
						listed contractors
					</li>
					<li>
						Homeowners are responsible for conducting their own due diligence before hiring any
						contractor
					</li>
					<li>
						We recommend obtaining multiple quotes, checking references, and verifying licenses and
						insurance
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, HPSC shall not be liable for any
					direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Use of or inability to use this website</li>
					<li>Reliance on any information provided on this website</li>
					<li>Services provided by contractors listed in our directory</li>
					<li>Errors, omissions, or inaccuracies in content</li>
					<li>Unauthorized access to or alteration of your data</li>
					<li>Any other matter relating to the website or our services</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Energy Savings Estimates</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					Any energy savings estimates, cost calculations, or performance projections provided on
					this website or by our programs are estimates only. Actual results will vary based on
					numerous factors including:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Home characteristics and condition</li>
					<li>Climate and weather conditions</li>
					<li>Occupant behavior and usage patterns</li>
					<li>Installation quality and maintenance</li>
					<li>Energy prices and rate structures</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					HPSC makes no guarantees regarding specific energy savings or financial returns.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Website Availability</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					We strive to maintain continuous availability of our website, but we do not guarantee that
					the website will be available at all times or that it will be free from errors, viruses,
					or other harmful components. We reserve the right to:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Modify or discontinue the website or any features without notice</li>
					<li>Restrict access to certain parts of the website</li>
					<li>Update or change content at any time</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Third-Party Content and Links</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					Our website may contain links to third-party websites or reference third-party products
					and services. These links and references are provided for convenience only:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>HPSC does not control or endorse third-party websites or content</li>
					<li>We are not responsible for the accuracy, legality, or content of external sites</li>
					<li>Inclusion of any link does not imply endorsement by HPSC</li>
					<li>You access third-party sites at your own risk</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Program Changes and Funding</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					Information about programs, incentives, rebates, and funding opportunities is subject to
					change without notice. Program availability, eligibility criteria, and funding amounts may
					be modified or discontinued based on:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Government policy changes</li>
					<li>Budget allocations and funding availability</li>
					<li>Partner organization decisions</li>
					<li>Program performance and demand</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					Always verify current program details and availability before making decisions based on
					this information.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Building Codes and Regulations</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					While we may provide information about building codes, regulations, and best practices,
					this information is general in nature. Building codes and regulations:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Vary by jurisdiction and are subject to change</li>
					<li>May have specific requirements for your location</li>
					<li>Should be verified with local authorities</li>
					<li>May require professional interpretation</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					Always consult with local building officials and qualified professionals to ensure
					compliance with applicable codes and regulations.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">No Warranty</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					This website and all information, content, and services are provided "as is" and "as
					available" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied, including but not
					limited to:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Warranties of merchantability</li>
					<li>Fitness for a particular purpose</li>
					<li>Non-infringement</li>
					<li>Title or compatibility</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Indemnification</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					By using this website, you agree to indemnify and hold harmless HPSC, its directors,
					officers, employees, partners, and agents from any claims, damages, losses, liabilities,
					and expenses (including legal fees) arising from:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
					<li>Your use of the website</li>
					<li>Your violation of these disclaimers or any applicable laws</li>
					<li>Your interactions with contractors or other users</li>
					<li>Any content you submit or transmit through the website</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Translation Disclaimer</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					If this website is available in multiple languages through translation services, please
					note that translations may not be entirely accurate. The English version of this website
					shall be considered the official and authoritative version in case of any discrepancies.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					If you have questions about these disclaimers, please contact us:
				</p>
				<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
					<p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold mb-2">Home Performance Stakeholder Council</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 mb-1">
						Email: <a href="mailto:info@homeperformance.ca" class="text-primary hover:underline"
							>info@homeperformance.ca</a
						>
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700 mb-1">Phone: 1-800-123-4567</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
